# The scenario suite is byte-stable: `python data/scenarios/generate.py --check`
# regenerates every artifact and compares bytes. The generator always writes
# LF-terminated JSON, so these files MUST stay LF on checkout regardless of
# core.autocrlf (Windows), or --check (and test_scenario_suite) would see CRLF
# drift. PDFs are binary — never touch their bytes.
*.json text eol=lf
*.py    text eol=lf
*.gitattributes text eol=lf
*.pdf   binary
